<h1>Donation Receipt</h1>

<p>Dear <%= @donor_name %>,</p>

<p>Thank you for your generous donation to California Kids Camp! Your support helps make our camp possible.</p>

<div class="receipt-box">
  <h2>Donation Details</h2>
  
  <div class="receipt-row">
    <span class="receipt-label">Donation ID:</span>
    <span class="receipt-value">#<%= @donation.id %></span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="receipt-row">
    <span class="receipt-label">Donation Date:</span>
    <span class="receipt-value"><%= @payment_date.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="receipt-row">
    <span class="receipt-label">Donor Name:</span>
    <span class="receipt-value"><%= @donor_name %></span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="receipt-row">
    <span class="receipt-label">Donor Email:</span>
    <span class="receipt-value"><%= @donor_email %></span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="receipt-row">
    <span class="receipt-label">Payment Status:</span>
    <span class="receipt-value"><%= @donation.payment_status.capitalize %></span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="receipt-row">
    <span class="receipt-label">Donation Amount:</span>
    <span class="receipt-value">$<%= sprintf("%.2f", @amount) %></span>
  </div>
</div>

<p>This receipt serves as confirmation of your donation. Please keep this email for your records.</p>

<p>Your generosity makes a real difference in the lives of the children who attend camp. Thank you again for your support!</p>

<p>Best regards,<br>
California Kids Camp Team</p>